369  double getTotalHeat() {
370  double const waterBoilTemp = 212.0; // Heat required temperature is 212.0°F
371 
372  // Heat required for removal of moisture
373  double hmv;
374  if (waterVaporDischargeTemperature < waterBoilTemp) {
375  // (H_mv )=m_st×(%w_i )×〖(t〗_wo-t_si)
376  hmv = chargeFeedRate * waterContentCharged * (waterVaporDischargeTemperature - initialTemperature);
377  } else {
378  double const specificHeatWaterVapor = 0.481;
379  double const waterEvaporation = 970.0; // Latent heat of evaporation for water is 970 Btu/lb
380  // (H_mv )=m_st×(%w_i )×(212-t_si )+m_st×(%w_i-%w_o ) ×[970+0.481×〖(t〗_wo-212)]
381  hmv = (chargeFeedRate * waterContentCharged * (waterBoilTemp - initialTemperature))
382  + chargeFeedRate * (waterContentCharged - waterContentDischarged)
383  * (waterEvaporation + specificHeatWaterVapor * (waterVaporDischargeTemperature - waterBoilTemp));
384  }
385  // (H_mr )=m_st×(%w_0 )×〖(t〗_wo-t_si)
386  double hmr = chargeFeedRate * waterContentDischarged * (waterVaporDischargeTemperature - waterBoilTemp);
387 
388  // Heat required for solid
389  double hs;
390  if (dischargeTemperature < meltingPoint) {
391  // (H_s)=m_st×(1-%w_i )×C_ps×(t_so-t_si)
392  hs = chargeFeedRate * (1.0 - waterContentCharged) * specificHeatSolid * (dischargeTemperature - initialTemperature);
393  } else {
394  // (H_s )=m_st×(1-%w_i )×C_ps×(T_sm-t_si )+h_m+C_(pl ×) (t_so-T_sm)
395  hs = chargeFeedRate * (1.0 - waterContentCharged)
396  * (specificHeatSolid * (meltingPoint - initialTemperature)
397  + (latentHeat * chargeMelted) + specificHeatLiquid * (dischargeTemperature - meltingPoint) * (chargeMelted)
398  + (specificHeatSolid * (1 - chargeMelted) * (dischargeTemperature - meltingPoint)));
399  }
400 
401  double heatReaction = 0.0;
402  if (thermicReactionType == LoadChargeMaterial::ThermicReactionType::ENDOTHERMIC) {
403  heatReaction = chargeFeedRate * (1.0 - waterContentCharged) * chargeReacted * reactionHeat;
404  }
405 
406  // H_t=H_mv+H_mr+H_s±H_r
407  totalHeat = hmv + hmr + hs + heatReaction + additionalHeat;
408  return totalHeat;
409  }
